Study Title: A Trial Comparing Adjuvant Oral UFT/LV to 5-FU/l-LV in Stage III Colorectal Cancer (JCOG-0205-MF)
Brief Summary: To evaluate the clinical effectiveness of oral UFT/LV comparing 5-FU/l-LV as adjuvant therapy for stage III colorectal cancer.
Primary Outcome Measures: Disease-free survival, during the study conduct
Secondary Outcome Measures: Overall survival, during the study conduct|Rate of adverse event, during the study conduct
Collaborators: Ministry of Health, Labour and Welfare, Japan
Study Design: Allocation: RANDOMIZED|Intervention Model: PARALLEL|Masking: NONE|Primary Purpose: TREATMENT
